        </div>
        <p>What started as cost-control has become cost-shifting. Employees face $3,000-8,000+ deductibles before insurance kicks in.</p>

        <h3>2. Prescription Drug Cost Crisis</h3>
        <div class="trend-card">
          <div class="trend-stat">45%</div>
          <div class="trend-desc">of Americans skip prescribed medications due to cost</div>
