        <h3>3. Provider Network Restrictions</h3>
        <p>Narrow networks force employees to choose between convenience/quality and staying "in-network" to avoid massive bills.</p>

        <h3>4. Mental Health Access Barriers</h3>
        <p>Average wait times for mental health appointments: 48 days. Many employees simply give up.</p>

